metadata.name: & sea 001
metadata.description:
This mysterious scenery appears only when the sunset and the low tide of the sea coincide.
You will feel as if you are the only one in the world.
The gentle sound of the waves and the sea breeze brushing your cheeks will make you feel comfortable and quiet.
What do you feel from this picture that looks like an animation?
I hope you like this NFT work.

Size : 5000 x 2812
Date : June , 2020
Location : Kagawa, Japan
